#services.services
  h1
    | Our 
    span.green Services 
    a.to-top(href='#header')  &#x25B2;
  p
    | Our core services include the following, and each is tailored to meet the specific needs of
    | healthcare providers, behavioral health organizations, and care delivery systems:
  .service-cards
    .service-card
      h2 Healthcare Staffing Solutions
      p
        | We provide healthcare organizations with highly qualified clinical and administrative
        | professionals who are ready to deliver. Whether short-term staffing support or long-term
        | placement is needed, our team matches the right talent with the right mission&mdash;ensuring
        | seamless continuity of care and operations.
    .service-card
      h2 Compliance Audits and Readiness Reviews
      p
        | Our audit support goes beyond box-checking. We conduct in-depth compliance reviews,
        | risk assessments, and mock audits to prepare your organization for state, federal, and
        | payer oversight. We help you find the gaps before the regulators do&mdash;and build corrective
        | action plans that work.
    .service-card
      h2 RFP Response Development
      p
        | We offer full-service support in writing and managing competitive responses to RFPs,
        | grants, and contracts. From strategy to submission, we craft proposals that reflect your
        | strengths, align with funder priorities, and give you the best chance at winning.
    .service-card
      h2  Program Development &amp; Implementation
      p
        | From concept to launch, we help organizations design, pilot, and scale new programs that
        | meet community needs and funding requirements. Our team handles all elements of
        | development&mdash;from regulatory compliance to staffing and workflows&mdash;so your vision
        | becomes a reality.
    .service-card
      h2  Staff Training &amp; Professional Development 
      p
        | We offer customized training modules and coaching that equip your workforce with the
        | tools they need to succeed. Whether clinical compliance, cultural competency, or
        | leadership training, we provide upskilling that&apos;s relevant, engaging, and rooted in real
        | world practice.
    .service-card
      h2 Accreditation Preparation 
      p
        | Achieving accreditation is a milestone&mdash;and we&apos;re here to walk you through every step. We
        | guide organizations through accreditation preparation for bodies like CARF, The Joint
        | Commission, NCQA, and others. From documentation to practice readiness, we ensure
        | you&apos;re not just prepared&mdash;you&apos;re confident.
    .service-card
      h2 Operations Management 
      p
        | Our consultants offer short- and long-term support for organizational operations,
        | including workflow optimization, strategic planning, and crisis response. We help you
        | identify inefficiencies, stabilize core systems, and build sustainable infrastructure for
        | future growth.
    .service-card
      h2 Clinical Research
      p
        | We support healthcare organizations in developing and operationalizing clinical research programs, with a focus on site readiness, sponsor engagement, and regulatory compliance. Our services include feasibility assessments, Principal Investigator alignment, study startup processes, and infrastructure development for Phase II–IV trials. We work closely with leadership and clinical teams to ensure research integration aligns with existing service lines while meeting sponsor and IRB expectations.
    .service-card
      h2 Quality Assurance
      p
        | We develop and implement Quality Assurance and Performance Improvement (QAPI) systems tailored to healthcare and behavioral health settings. This includes audit readiness preparation, documentation review processes, internal monitoring tools, and corrective action planning. We ensure organizations maintain continuous compliance while using data to drive measurable improvements in service delivery.
#dialog-form(title='Book a Call')
  p.validateTips All form fields are required.
  form
    fieldset
      label(for='name') Name
      input#name.text.ui-widget-content.ui-corner-all(type='text' name='name')
      br
      label(for='email') Email
      input#email.text.ui-widget-content.ui-corner-all(type='text' name='email')
      br
      label(for='phone') Phone
      input#phone.text.ui-widget-content.ui-corner-all(type='phone' name='phone')
      br
      // Allow form submission with keyboard without duplicating the dialog button
      input(type='submit' tabindex='-1' style='position:absolute; top:-1000px')
footer.footer
  span &copy; 2025 Urgent Mindset. All Rights Reserved
  img.logo(src='static/img/UM Icon Light.png')
